OL,3,CRoyal Mail takeover by Czech
OL,4,Cbillionaire given Government approval
OL,6,FThe deal between Kretinsky and Royal
OL,7,FMail's parent company is #3.6 billion
OL,8,F` or #5.3 billion including debt, ITV
OL,9,FNews Caroline Lewis reports
OL,11,FThe sale of Royal Mail's parent
OL,12,Fcompany to a Czech billionaire has
OL,13,Fbeen approved by the Government
OL,14,Fputting the postal service into
OL,15,Fforeign ownership for the first time.
OL,17,FThe takeover by Daniel Kretinsky's EP
OL,18,FGroup from current owner International
OL,19,FDistribution Services was confirmed by
OL,20,FBusiness Secretary Jonathan Reynolds
OL,21,Fon Monday morning.
