OL,3,CRoyal Mail takeover by Czech
OL,4,Cbillionaire given Government approval
OL,6,FHe said the takeover was secured along
OL,7,Fwith legally binding commitments with
OL,8,FMr Kretinsky's EPH Group over the
OL,9,Fpostal service, including protecting
OL,10,Fthe one-price-goes-anywhere delivery
OL,11,Fcommitment and a pledge to keep Royal
OL,12,FMail headquartered in the UK.
OL,14,FMr Kretinsky is believed to have made
OL,15,Fseveral other concessions to gain
OL,16,Fapproval, including allowing workers
OL,17,Fto get a 10% share of any dividends
OL,18,Fpaid out to him and giving the
OL,19,FGovernment a "golden share" in the
OL,20,Fpostal service.
