OL,6,FHe also committed not to raid the
OL,7,Fpensions surplus, to maintain the
OL,8,Funiversal service and the brand name,
OL,9,Fplus to keep tax residency in the UK
OL,10,Ffor five years.
OL,12,FMr Reynolds said: "For too many years
OL,13,Fprogress on securing a stable future
OL,14,Fat Royal Mail has stalled, but from
OL,15,Fday one we have been committed to
OL,16,Fproviding a secure future for
OL,17,Fthousands of workers and customers."
